    L07_P1_p1: "Have you ever noticed that red and yellow are often used for warning signs? Vivid and warm colors are chosen because they catch people’s attention. They help people notice signs whose messages should be understood immediately.",
    L07_P1_p2: "Besides the choice of colors, the contrast of colors plays an important role in conveying messages clearly and quickly. For example, emergency exit signs show a picture of a green figure on a white background. The contrast between green and white parts helps us distinguish the figure clearly from its background even in smoke or fire.",
    L07_P1_full: "Have you ever noticed that red and yellow are often used for warning signs? Vivid and warm colors are chosen because they catch people’s attention. They help people notice signs whose messages should be understood immediately.<br><br>Besides the choice of colors, the contrast of colors plays an important role in conveying messages clearly and quickly. For example, emergency exit signs show a picture of a green figure on a white background. The contrast between green and white parts helps us distinguish the figure clearly from its background even in smoke or fire.",

    L07_P2_p1: "Colors have various effects on us. Let’s look at the effects of white. The two go stones in the photo seem to be the same size, but actually they are not. The white stone is made slightly smaller because of the fact that white objects look larger than they really are.",
    L07_P2_p2: "The effects of colors are also important when grocery stores sell fresh fruit or vegetables. For example, oranges are sold in bright red mesh bags because red makes the color of the fruit look more vivid. For the same reason, okra is sold in green mesh bags. In this way, fruit and vegetables look fresher and more delicious. This stimulates consumers to buy them.",
    L07_P2_full: "Colors have various effects on us. Let’s look at the effects of white. The two go stones in the photo seem to be the same size, but actually they are not. The white stone is made slightly smaller because of the fact that white objects look larger than they really are.<br><br>The effects of colors are also important when grocery stores sell fresh fruit or vegetables. For example, oranges are sold in bright red mesh bags because red makes the color of the fruit look more vivid. For the same reason, okra is sold in green mesh bags. In this way, fruit and vegetables look fresher and more delicious. This stimulates consumers to buy them.",

    L07_P3_p1: "Companies often pay attention to the psychological effects of colors. They consider the colors of a package to attract customers. For example, gold is a packaging color of which people have a positive image as “effective” or “special.” In a study conducted by a drug company, one out of four people answered that they would choose a product if the color of the package was gold.",
    L07_P3_p2: "When companies choose the main color of their logos, they take the impact and image of the color into consideration. Food companies often use red in their logos. It makes customers excited and hungry. If a company is highly conscious of the environment, green is a natural choice. Green reminds people of nature.",
    L07_P3_full: "Companies often pay attention to the psychological effects of colors. They consider the colors of a package to attract customers. For example, gold is a packaging color of which people have a positive image as “effective” or “special.” In a study conducted by a drug company, one out of four people answered that they would choose a product if the color of the package was gold.<br><br>When companies choose the main color of their logos, they take the impact and image of the color into consideration. Food companies often use red in their logos. It makes customers excited and hungry. If a company is highly conscious of the environment, green is a natural choice. Green reminds people of nature.",

    L07_P4_p1: "Considering the choice of colors is useful when you want to create a comfortable atmosphere in your house. According to the purpose, choose a different color for your room, where you usually spend most of your time.",
    L07_P4_p2: "When you need to concentrate on your studies, choose blue. It makes you feel calm. If you want to feel relaxed, choose brown, the color of soil. It is believed to have a healing power. If you want to feel refreshed and clean, white is a good choice. It also makes your room look more spacious.",
    L07_P4_p3: "Now that you know some secrets of colors, you can use this knowledge to enhance the quality of your life.",
    L07_P4_full: "Considering the choice of colors is useful when you want to create a comfortable atmosphere in your house. According to the purpose, choose a different color for your room, where you usually spend most of your time.<br><br>When you need to concentrate on your studies, choose blue. It makes you feel calm. If you want to feel relaxed, choose brown, the color of soil. It is believed to have a healing power. If you want to feel refreshed and clean, white is a good choice. It also makes your room look more spacious.<br><br>Now that you know some secrets of colors, you can use this knowledge to enhance the quality of your life.",

